  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct. The FEA model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two laboratories. All 13 V&V 40 factors assessed; one factor (Test conditions) below required level due to single test condition. Intended use is pre-market submission support for Class II spinal fixation devices under 21 CFR 888.3070; the model predicts construct stiffness and yield load under quasi-static compression-bending in accordance with ASTM F1717-15. Scope is limited to non-cannulated 7.5 mm titanium alloy screws at L4-L5 level with polyaxial heads.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/nagaraja-f1717-compression-bending-req-001",
