      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for model risk level 3.",
      "rationale": "Benchmark problems from NAFEMS and Ansys verification manual confirmed correct implementation of linear elastic and contact formulations. Results matched analytical solutions within 0.5% for canonical beam-bending cases."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
