      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for model risk level 3.",
      "rationale": "Independent peer review of model setup, boundary conditions, and load application performed by a second engineer not involved in model development. Checklist-based review documented; no critical use errors identified."
