      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for model risk level 3.",
      "rationale": "Linear elastic constitutive model justified by experimental observation that yield occurs at large displacements not reached in the primary comparison window. Contact modeled with augmented Lagrangian formulation; geometric nonlinearity included. Model form assumptions documented and supported by literature."
    },
    {
