      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for model risk level 3.",
      "rationale": "Material properties (Ti-6Al-4V: E=114 GPa, nu=0.34) sourced from ASTM F136 and confirmed by coupon testing from the same material lot. UHMWPE block modulus characterized by compression testing per ASTM D695. Geometric inputs derived from CMM measurements of physical constructs."
