      "factorType": "Test samples",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for model risk level 3.",
      "rationale": "N=11 physical constructs assembled from production-representative screws and rods. Sample size supports statistical characterization of variability. Constructs span two independent laboratories to assess inter-lab reproducibility. Dimensional inspection confirmed geometric conformance."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for model risk level 3.",
      "rationale": "Testing conducted at a single load rate and single environmental condition (ambient, dry). ASTM F1717 specifies quasi-static loading only; no cyclic or temperature-varied conditions explored. Achieved level is below required due to this single-condition limitation, representing a known gap accepted by the credibility assessment team."
    },
    {
