      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level for model risk level 3.",
      "rationale": "Model input parameters mapped directly to experimentally measured quantities for each of the 11 constructs. Screw geometry, rod diameter, and block modulus individualized per specimen. Traceability matrix documents correspondence between experimental measurements and model inputs."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
